item.title: CVE-2020-8105|2024-08-04T09:48:25.638Z -- abode -- iota%20all-in-one%20security%20kit
item.description: OS Command Injection vulnerability in the wirelessConnect handler of Abode iota All-In-One Security Kit allows an attacker to inject commands and gain root access. This issue affects: Abode iota All-In-One Security Kit versions prior to 1.0.2.23_6.9V_dev_t2_homekit_RF_2.0.19_s2_kvsABODE oz.
